You can customize this without it being added to core by doing:

``` js
_.iteratee = _.wrap(_.iteratee, function(iteratee, func) {
  return (typeof func == 'string' && /^::/.test(func))
     ? _.method(func.replace(/^::/, ''))
     : iteratee(func);
});
```

