By moving the null checks a bit lower

``` js
if (value > other || !valIsReflexive || (value === undefined && othIsReflexive)) {
  return 1;
}
if (value < other || !othIsReflexive || (other === undefined && valIsReflexive)) {
  return -1;
}
if (value === null) {
  return -1;
}
